                <p>Visitors to the Vikramshila Archaeological Museum can enjoy guided tours led by knowledgeable staff, providing insights into the history and significance of the exhibits. The museum is wheelchair accessible and offers amenities such as a wheelchair-accessible entrance, exit, and parking.</p>
